'''Carlos Acevedo López''' (born 19 April 1996) is a Mexican professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Liga MX]] club [[Santos Laguna]], whom he [[Captain (association football)|captains]], and the [[Mexico national football team|Mexico national team]].

==Club career==
Acevedo made his [[Liga MX]] debut with [[Santos Laguna]] on 20 August 2016 in a match against [[Cruz Azul]] which resulted in a 3–1 defeat.<ref>{{cite web|title=Historia de vida: Carlos Acevedo fue corrido por Santos y ahora es titular|url=https://www.tudn.com/futbol/liga-mx/historia-de-vida-carlos-acevedo-fue-corrido-por-santos-y-ahora-es-titular|work=TUDN|date=6 August 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref>

Prior to the start of the [[2020–21 Liga MX season#Torneo Guardianes 2021|2021 Guardianes tournament]], club manager [[Guillermo Almada]] named him as [[Captain (association football)|captain]] following the departure of former captain [[Julio Furch]] to sibling club [[Atlas F.C.|Atlas]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Guillermo Almada reveló las razones por las que Carlos Acevedo fue el capitán de Santos contra Cruz Azul|url=https://www.infobae.com/america/deportes/2021/01/11/guillermo-almada-revelo-las-razones-por-las-que-carlos-acevedo-fue-el-capitan-de-santos-contra-cruz-azul/|work=Infobae|date=11 January 2021|language=Spanish}}</ref>

On 10 September 2022, Acevedo scored a header against [[Querétaro F.C.|Querétaro]] during the 99th minute of the match, helping Santos secure a 3-3 draw.<ref>{{cite web|title=¡INCREÍBLE! Gol de Carlos Acevedo rescata a Santos de Querétaro|url= https://onefootball.com/es/noticias/increible-gol-de-carlos-acevedo-rescata-a-santos-de-queretaro-35816580|work=Infobae|date=11 September 2021|language=Spanish}}</ref>

==International career==
In December 2021, Acevedo received his first call-up to the [[Mexico national football team|senior national team]] by [[Gerardo Martino]], and made his debut on 8 December 2021, in a friendly match against [[Chile national football team|Chile]].<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.fanbolero.com/2021/12/checa-la-convocatoria-de-mexico-para-enfrentar-a-chile/|title= ¡Checa la convocatoria de México para enfrentar a Chile!|website= fanbolero.com|date= December 6, 2021|access-date= December 7, 2021|archive-date= December 7, 2021|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211207181234/https://www.fanbolero.com/2021/12/checa-la-convocatoria-de-mexico-para-enfrentar-a-chile/|url-status= dead}}</ref>

In June 2024, Acevedo was called up by [[Jaime Lozano]] to the [[Copa America 2024|2024 Copa America]] following the injury of the starting goalkeeper [[Luis Malagón]]. He was not involved in any games during the tournament.

